<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>纽约时报 &amp;gt; 美国 &amp;gt; 政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/on-politics</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 22:19:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普的主要批评者、众议员托马斯·马西能在肯塔基州初选中坚持下去吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/thomas-massie-trump.html</link><description>任何共和党人都可以不同意特朗普的观点并侥幸逃脱惩罚吗？托马斯·马西在肯塔基州的初选是一个关键考验。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 22:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/thomas-massie-trump.html</guid></item><item><title>这是美国的一个混乱时刻。这不是共和党人需要的。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/republicans-trump-midterms.html</link><description>重大选举前的全国性不安和焦虑情绪对执政党来说很少有好处。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 22:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/republicans-trump-midterms.html</guid></item><item><title>加州可以通过“丛林初选”选举共和党州长</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/20/us/politics/california-primary-gop-governors-race.html</link><description>该州完全开放的“丛林初选”让民主党人感到紧张。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 21:18:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/20/us/politics/california-primary-gop-governors-race.html</guid></item><item><title>伊利诺伊州比赛最热闹的结果</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/18/us/politics/what-happened-illinois-election.html</link><description>以下是候选人观看派对上最佳复出、最自豪的州长和最昂贵的水的摘要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 13:52:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/18/us/politics/what-happened-illinois-election.html</guid></item><item><title>伊利诺伊州初选民主党内讧的内幕</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/illinois-democrat-primary-brandon-herrera-mamdani.html</link><description>我们与皮奥里亚出生的记者谈论了他所说的美国最好的州的小学日。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 21:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/illinois-democrat-primary-brandon-herrera-mamdani.html</guid></item><item><title>关于选举季人工智能政治竞选广告的了解</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/13/us/politics/ai-ads-campaign-deepfake.html</link><description>等等，那不是真正的詹姆斯·塔拉里科……</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 22:13:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/13/us/politics/ai-ads-campaign-deepfake.html</guid></item><item><title>一些民主党人已经在考虑南卡罗来纳州 2028 年的初选</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/11/us/politics/south-carolina-primary-democrats-2028.html</link><description>该州 2028 年的初选可能很重要，并且已经引起了一些民主党人的关注。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 22:26:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/11/us/politics/south-carolina-primary-democrats-2028.html</guid></item><item><title>民主党关注经济，伊朗战争给中期选举蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/09/us/politics/iran-war-midterm-election-economy.html</link><description>民主党人专注于经济，而共和党人希望他们专注于经济。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 22:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/09/us/politics/iran-war-midterm-election-economy.html</guid></item><item><title>塔拉里科的社交媒体论文线索、就业报告和更多政治新闻</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/06/us/politics/talarico-social-media-democrats-jobs-report.html</link><description>对于一些民主党人来说，世代更迭伴随着令人尴尬的社交媒体过去。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 22:49:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/06/us/politics/talarico-social-media-democrats-jobs-report.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普领导下的德克萨斯州下一步会怎样？ 4 个大问题。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/politics/trump-texas-paxton-talarico-house-runoff.html</link><description>最直接的问题是：特朗普会做什么？</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 23:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/politics/trump-texas-paxton-talarico-house-runoff.html</guid></item></channel></rss>